title: Your score is on the way...
body: Get good rest today, and check back soon! Sleep, resting heart rate, and heart rate variability impact your readiness to train. Personalizing your score takes time.

title: Your target load is on the way...
body: Your target load is personalized based on your age, gender, and heart rate during physical activity. Along with readiness, this target load helps you plan your workouts.
